<h2 class="bold font-l">"We'll have you flying"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Empire has some nice recruiting advertisements. Cut to three years later, with troopers unglamorously dying in the mud on Mimban and Han trying to survive in this hell. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/JoinTheArmyTheySaid" class='trope-example-link'>"Join the Army," They Said</a></p>
</div>
